  "detailed_description": "<h1>Update Notes</h1><p>Soon, we'll implement a challenge mode, with new levels, new bonuses and weekly challenges !</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Explore a house in search of Leonardo's memories.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/501f71b0d50b933df9c91afcd3fe7a46.poster.avif?t=1771423565\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/501f71b0d50b933df9c91afcd3fe7a46.webm?t=1771423565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/501f71b0d50b933df9c91afcd3fe7a46.mp4?t=1771423565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Souvenirs</strong> is a merge like strategy game, created by a tiny independent French studio.<br>Merge objects in distorded containers and unlock the story of the painter Leonardo and his family.<br><br>You can use limited bonuses as well as a chance to continue the level by spending in-game currency which is unlocked by scoring and completing levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br>- <strong>The Anvil</strong> makes the item in hand very heavy and allows it to reach the bottom of the playing area (if you are lucky!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/33f4a80e1b04dc66cca4fa1b6657158d.avif?t=1771423565\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>- <strong>The Slingshot</strong> allows you to remove a specific object by targeting it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/74b009861ba5de6b5d2bb2b30b59d122.avif?t=1771423565\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>- <strong>The Upgrade</strong> allows the object in hand to evolve into its next form.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/e293b05b7063b969184c57418e7ca6b7.avif?t=1771423565\" width=128 height=128 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Explore a house in search of Leonardo's memories.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/501f71b0d50b933df9c91afcd3fe7a46.poster.avif?t=1771423565\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/501f71b0d50b933df9c91afcd3fe7a46.webm?t=1771423565\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/501f71b0d50b933df9c91afcd3fe7a46.mp4?t=1771423565\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Souvenirs</strong> is a merge like strategy game, created by a tiny independent French studio.<br>Merge objects in distorded containers and unlock the story of the painter Leonardo and his family.<br><br>You can use limited bonuses as well as a chance to continue the level by spending in-game currency which is unlocked by scoring and completing levels.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br>- <strong>The Anvil</strong> makes the item in hand very heavy and allows it to reach the bottom of the playing area (if you are lucky!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/33f4a80e1b04dc66cca4fa1b6657158d.avif?t=1771423565\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>- <strong>The Slingshot</strong> allows you to remove a specific object by targeting it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026350/extras/74b009861ba5de6b5d2bb2b30b59d122.avif?t=1771423565\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><br>- <strong>The Upgrade</strong> allows the object in hand to evolve into its next form.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/app